description: The successor to AlphaGo is being used to create a more efficient type of video compression.
title: DeepMind's AI agent MuZero could turbocharge YouTube
title_page: DeepMind's AI agent MuZero could turbocharge YouTube - BBC News
maintext: DeepMind is not the first to try and create an agent that both models the dynamics of the environment it is placed in and carries out tree searches - deciding how to proceed by looking several steps ahead to determine the best outcome.
